  "detailed_description": "Jump Tale is a simple <strong>2D Platformer</strong> with <strong>10</strong> different playable “Characters”. It's your Goal to finish all the <strong>110</strong> Levels with the best possible time and the least possible deaths.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 11 Different Worlds<br></li><li> 10 Different Characters<br></li><li> 110 Levels in Total<br></li><li> Switches between Characters in Levels<br></li><li> Different dangers to dodge<br></li><li> Time and Death tracking</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Can you beat the levels with the least deaths possible?<br></li><li> Can you beat your own best times and always get faster?<br></li><li> Post your score in the Community hub!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Jump Tale is a simple <strong>2D Platformer</strong> with <strong>10</strong> different playable “Characters”. It's your Goal to finish all the <strong>110</strong> Levels with the best possible time and the least possible deaths.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 11 Different Worlds<br></li><li> 10 Different Characters<br></li><li> 110 Levels in Total<br></li><li> Switches between Characters in Levels<br></li><li> Different dangers to dodge<br></li><li> Time and Death tracking</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Can you beat the levels with the least deaths possible?<br></li><li> Can you beat your own best times and always get faster?<br></li><li> Post your score in the Community hub!</li></ul>",
